    <p>When: To­mor­row, 4pm Sus­tain­abil­ity has been a per­ti­nent is­sue in the fash­ion in­dus­try in re­cent years, even more so with the pan­demic.</p>
    <p>How do vir­tual fash­ion shows like this, which re­duces the car­bon foot­print of fly­ing peo­ple around the world, play a part?</p>
    <p>All things eco-friendly are brought to the fore in this panel dis­cus­sion fronted by sus­tain­abil­ity plat­form Green Is The New Black founder Stephanie Dick­son, de­signer Jude Ng and the ac­ces­sory artist of la­bel The Kang.</p>


